06:20.600 --> 06:21.700
ok. so,
what's the weird part?

06:21.700 --> 06:24.500
i wanted to determine
if malnutrition played a part in his death.

06:24.500 --> 06:26.900
so, i looked for evidence
of starvation ketosis

06:26.900 --> 06:30.700
by analyzing some vitreous humor--
the squishy part OF THE EYEBALL

06:30.800 --> 06:32.900
and i couldn't find
any ketone bodies there.

06:33.100 --> 06:33.700
meaning?

06:33.700 --> 06:35.500
he was getting
nutrients somehow.

06:35.800 --> 06:36.400
through an i.v.?

06:36.400 --> 06:37.800
there were no marks
to indicate that.

06:37.800 --> 06:39.200
any idea
what else could it be?

06:39.200 --> 06:41.300
honestly, i have no idea.

06:43.800 --> 06:44.700
CRIME SCENE DO NOT CROSS

06:44.700 --> 06:47.700
not exactly
a well-preserved scene.

06:47.800 --> 06:49.600
it's the crime scene
investigators.

06:49.700 --> 06:52.000
they all want to play cop instead of just being
scientists--

06:52.000 --> 06:54.000
and they end up trampling
on everything.

06:54.800 --> 06:58.800
so, he suffocates the boy at another location,
prepares the body,

06:58.800 --> 07:01.800
takes him out to the middle
of nowhere and dumps him.

07:01.800 --> 07:05.200
except there were no traces of the unsub's sweat
on the boy's clothing.

07:05.200 --> 07:05.900
what are you getting at?

07:05.900 --> 07:07.800
well, it's like 1,000 degrees
out here.

07:07.800 --> 07:12.000
if he carried the body,
then he would have gotten
traces of sweat on the clothes.

07:12.100 --> 07:13.300
so, he wraps him
in something.

07:13.400 --> 07:14.700
no fibers.

07:14.800 --> 07:20.300
so, he took the time to change the boy's clothing 
and groom him ONCE HE GOT HERE.

07:20.900 --> 07:24.200
if he took that much time,
he'd have to do it at night.

07:24.700 --> 07:28.300
but you still run the risk of someone recalling your
car once the body's found.

07:28.800 --> 07:31.000
not if you didn't have
to park it by the road.

07:33.800 --> 07:36.600
well, you'd want to park a distance away from the dump site

07:36.600 --> 07:40.300
just in case someone saw the car 
and came to see what you were up to.

07:40.800 --> 07:41.800
now, tell me this.

07:41.800 --> 07:45.300
<i>if you can drive out
into the desert to dump a body,</i>

07:45.300 --> 07:48.200
why not go in deeper, where you 
won't be seen from the road?

07:48.900 --> 07:52.000
because he wanted to be able to drive by and see the body.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.300
that's why he groomed him.

07:54.000 --> 07:56.300
it's like he was preparing him
for a funeral.

08:00.400 --> 08:02.400
yeah. i got it.

08:02.900 --> 08:03.900
thank you.

