we feel like
it's a viable plan.

15:51.400 --> 15:55.600
 you're asking us to go to
the funeral of a 5-year-old boy.

15:55.800 --> 15:57.900
we're going to watch them
lower his body into the ground.

15:57.900 --> 16:00.500
<i>and the same man
who killed him has our son.</i>

