we're looking for anything that
might draw him out.

16:06.000 --> 16:09.100
i can't watch them bury
a child knowing that we're next.

16:09.100 --> 16:11.800
we feel like this plan
has a reasonable chance SUCCESS.

16:11.800 --> 16:18.500
what do you consider a reasonable chance 
that i will ever see my son again? 10%? 20?

16:18.700 --> 16:20.000
i can't give you numbers.

16:20.900 --> 16:21.700
you could.

16:23.300 --> 16:24.900
i understand
if you can't do this.

16:26.100 --> 16:28.800
but if you can, we need to talk about 
who we're looking for.

16:30.900 --> 16:32.700
we believe the man
we're looking for is white.

16:32.700 --> 16:34.900
he's probably in his
late 20s to mid-30s.

16:34.900 --> 16:37.900
judging by the quality of the clothing he put
his first victim in,

16:37.900 --> 16:40.200
we believe he comes from
a middle-class background.

16:40.300 --> 16:43.600
this is not someone who is going to be 
at the funeral in a high-end or well tailored suit.

16:43.600 --> 16:45.200
he also might be paying
a lot of attention

16:45.200 --> 16:47.700
to the parents of the most
recent boy to be abducted.

16:47.700 --> 16:51.700
<i>watch for anyone whose focus 
is on them instead of the service itself.</i>

16:51.700 --> 16:54.800
we also believe he may drive
a 4-wheel-drive vehicle.

16:54.800 --> 16:56.700
pay extra attention
to those mourners.

